{
  "amplifyuibuilder.component.actionparameters.CfnAbout": "Represents the event action configuration for an element of a `Component` or `ComponentChild`. Use for the workflow feature in Amplify Studio that allows you to bind events and actions to components. `ActionParameters` defines the action that is performed when an event occurs on the component.",
